---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section class="pt-[25vh] pb-12 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <img src={`/doctordaddysir-site/images/pentai-logo.png`} alt="Pentai logo" />

    <p class="text-lg mb-4">
      Pentai is a red-team–first, AI-augmented penetration testing framework designed for serious operators.
      It's built around a terminal-native, tmux-based workflow that keeps AI in the background — and control in your hands.
    </p>

    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3">
      <li>Operator-driven: AI supports, never overrides</li>
      <li>Immutable log streams, timestamps, and audit trails</li>
      <li>Plugin architecture for extensibility</li>
      <li>Tool integrity checks via binary hashing</li>
      <li>Smart plugin system, finding manager, and report generation</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-6">
      <a href="https://github.com/DoctorDaddySir/Pentai" target="_blank" class="underline hover:text-accent">
        View on GitHub →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
